{
  "stem": "24515.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then it occurred to me, I was in Holland, no Nazi would get after me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a feeling then, which also have never forgotten, and it's strong with me today-- I knew that I would never, ever, live again under the kind of circumstances, the totalitarianism, and so on, that I was leaving.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was very strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Very shortly, we rolled into a Dutch station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were all kinds of ladies there who fed us candy, and cookies, and drinks, and so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just want to go back because I'm-- I'm not really clear on one thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- tell me about the selection process.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Would you know anything about the selection process for the Kinder--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do know that my father felt a little bit bad about my being chosen because he had gone to Berlin, to these people, and in a sense, complained that nobody from our area had ever been chosen.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the next time-- round, I was chosen, which wasn't his intention, or his-- and he-- he just didn't know that was because of his-- him anyway, but I know he felt a bit bad about that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, look-- it's-- it's very difficult to explain this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was 16.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was a-- I was an immature 16.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had been-- I was bright, right, I mean, I could tell you all about Latin, and Aristotle, and so and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was an immature youngster, who had been, as I told you many times, protected very carefully from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the-- you know, from the unpleasant events of the day-- had been a very spoiled kid.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
